{"tid":1980868,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：憂個人資料被武器化 黨衛軍展示記者證件事件受疫情影響仍需數月調查","createTime":"2020-04-20T10:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T10:48:15.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"70ec69c4ab5183dfad975fe4485ba94c9c592cfd","tid":1980868,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:45:03.000Z","msg":"私隱專員調查警員涉將記者證件公開展示 數月內有結果<br />\n20.04.2020 18:38<br />\n<br />\n私隱專員黃繼兒表示，就警員涉嫌在直播鏡頭前，公開展示一個記者身份證的事件，調查已接近最後階段，但由於疫情影響工作進度，預計幾個月內會有最終的調查結果和報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282158&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282158%26csid%3D261_341&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPsmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=53e232e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282158&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n黃繼兒：個人資料被武器化 問題嚴重性史無前例<br />\n20.04.2020 16:50<br />\n<br />\n個人資料私隱專員黃繼兒，在立法會一個委員會簡報去年工作，指本港去年「起底」數字及嚴重性是史無前例，累積投訴個案近 5,000 宗，涉及警員起底佔36%，當中曾表態支持和反對政府人士各佔30%。自去年6月反修例事件後，單一個月的投訴數案，已超出前8年的總和。黃繼兒認為個人資料有被武器化的現象，情況相當嚴重，值得關注。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會陸頌雄關注，警方去年就「起底」拘捕8人，只有一人被起訴，擔心檢控率低，是否能保障被起底人士；民主黨黃碧雲關注，警方如將遊行集會期間收集的示威者資料，傳輸到內地是否涉及私穩問題。黃繼兒指無收過相關投訴，又指檢控率或是證據不足，公署已將 1400多宗涉嫌違反刑事條例的起底個案，交警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282139&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282139%26csid%3D261_341&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPsmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=dd23aa1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282139&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"8293b7d679550934d08f9f8cba5d847372ff2745","tid":1980868,"uid":50891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:48:15.000Z","msg":"公署已將 1400多宗涉嫌違反刑事條例的起底個案，交警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}